WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:00:25.943 --> 00:00:27.695
Raziel!

3
00:00:28.703 --> 00:00:32.332
Fin Raziel!
I have to talk to you. please!

4
00:00:43.663 --> 00:00:45.699
She's not here.

5
00:00:51.543 --> 00:00:54.933
Get back! Who are you?

6
00:00:56.023 --> 00:00:58.742
Who are you?

7
00:01:01.143 --> 00:01:04.021
- I'm Willow Ufgood.
- What are you doing here?

8
00:01:04.143 --> 00:01:07.613
I've come to find
the great sorceress Fin Raziel.

9
00:01:07.743 --> 00:01:10.177
That's me! I'm Raziel!

10
00:01:12.143 --> 00:01:13.974
This can't be right!

11
00:01:14.103 --> 00:01:17.413
One of Bavmorda's spells
transformed me.

12
00:01:19.663 --> 00:01:22.097
Believe me.
it could have been worse!

13
00:01:23.623 --> 00:01:27.741
Well. this wand is for you.
It's from Cherlindrea.

14
00:01:27.863 --> 00:01:29.933
Then the prophecy is true.

15
00:01:30.063 --> 00:01:33.419
The princess has been born.
Take me to her.

16
00:01:37.263 --> 00:01:40.380
It is Elora Danan.
Isn't she beautiful?

17
00:01:42.183 --> 00:01:44.981
Isn't she beautiful?

18
00:01:45.103 --> 00:01:47.697
- That's Raziel?
- I don't know.

19
00:01:47.823 --> 00:01:50.576
I expected something
more grand. Less...

20
00:01:50.703 --> 00:01:52.580
- Fuzzy.
- Fuzzy.

21
00:01:52.703 --> 00:01:56.298
You must use the wand.
Turn me back into my human form.

22
00:01:56.423 --> 00:01:59.574
- What do I do?
- You mean you're not a sorcerer?

23
00:02:00.863 --> 00:02:03.172
Yes. Sorta.

24
00:02:03.303 --> 00:02:04.577
I'm a farmer.

25
00:02:05.823 --> 00:02:08.383
- But I do know a few tricks.
- Tricks?

26
00:02:08.503 --> 00:02:12.735
Cherlindrea sent you?
You must learn real magic.

27
00:02:14.583 --> 00:02:16.778
- Horses!
- Horses!

28
00:02:16.903 --> 00:02:19.098
Quick! Take her! Hurry!

29
00:02:27.783 --> 00:02:30.581
I knew he was a traitor!

30
00:02:33.143 --> 00:02:35.577
- Sorry about this. peck.
- Keep your mouth shut.

31
00:02:36.823 --> 00:02:39.291
I told you we'd find them
without your help.

32
00:02:39.423 --> 00:02:41.300
- Give me that baby!
- No!

33
00:02:44.663 --> 00:02:48.417
- Give her back!
- Leave me alone! Don't touch me!

34
00:02:54.143 --> 00:02:55.895
This is the one
we're looking for.

35
00:02:56.023 --> 00:02:57.979
We must take it back
to Nockmaar.

36
00:03:01.943 --> 00:03:03.740
Lose your skirt?

37
00:03:11.583 --> 00:03:14.461
- I've still got what counts.
- Not for long.

38
00:03:20.863 --> 00:03:23.252
- Bring him.
- Over here!

39
00:03:41.263 --> 00:03:43.618
We'll never keep up
with those horses.

40
00:03:44.343 --> 00:03:47.255
- Then we will have to track them.
- That would take forever.

41
00:03:47.383 --> 00:03:49.851
Besides. even if we find them.
they'll catch us...

42
00:03:49.983 --> 00:03:53.020
stick us in cages. torture us
and finally devour us.

43
00:03:53.143 --> 00:03:54.940
Are you suggesting we go home?

44
00:03:55.063 --> 00:03:57.702
- Nah. This is more fun.
- All right.

45
00:03:57.823 --> 00:03:59.700
Fine. then.
Come on.

46
00:04:13.063 --> 00:04:16.294
I'm worried about Elora.
She doesn't sound good.

47
00:04:16.423 --> 00:04:19.017
Hurry! Practise
the chant I taught you!

48
00:04:20.103 --> 00:04:22.571
Tanna looatha...

49
00:04:22.703 --> 00:04:24.659
I can't remember
the middle part.

50
00:04:24.783 --> 00:04:26.660
Locktwaar!

51
00:04:26.783 --> 00:04:29.661
That's the word
that pleads for change.

52
00:04:29.783 --> 00:04:31.660
Locktwaar.

53
00:04:35.143 --> 00:04:38.101
Elora's cold and hungry.
She knows me.

54
00:04:38.223 --> 00:04:40.054
Please. let me take care of her.

55
00:04:40.183 --> 00:04:42.174
I don't need help from a peck.

56
00:04:46.583 --> 00:04:49.541
- What are you staring at?
- Your leg.

57
00:04:50.663 --> 00:04:52.574
I'd like to break it.

58
00:04:52.703 --> 00:04:54.580
You may find that difficult.
slave...

59
00:04:54.703 --> 00:04:56.739
while I'm up here
and you're down there.

60
00:04:59.743 --> 00:05:01.859
I hate that woman.

61
00:05:38.863 --> 00:05:40.819
I found it. Kael.

62
00:05:43.183 --> 00:05:45.492
That should make
my mother happy.

63
00:05:45.623 --> 00:05:47.500
What are they gonna do to her?

64
00:06:00.543 --> 00:06:03.057
Hither walha...

65
00:06:03.183 --> 00:06:06.493
bairn deru bordak...

66
00:06:06.623 --> 00:06:07.897
bellanockt.

67
00:06:09.383 --> 00:06:11.260
That's magic?
Smells terrible.

68
00:06:11.383 --> 00:06:14.420
- It's the life spark. It forms after...
- It stinks!

69
00:06:14.543 --> 00:06:17.535
- This whole thing stinks!
- Ignore him. Willow.

70
00:06:17.663 --> 00:06:20.541
- He's a fool!
- If only I had a sword!

71
00:06:21.663 --> 00:06:23.574
If only you'd quit
talking about it.

72
00:06:23.703 --> 00:06:26.854
Willow. you must transform me
to my human self.

73
00:06:26.983 --> 00:06:29.656
But. Raziel. I'm not ready yet.

74
00:06:29.783 --> 00:06:32.820
You'd better be.
Get me down.

75
00:06:36.343 --> 00:06:37.617
Ow!

76
00:06:41.143 --> 00:06:44.021
Why don't you help me get out of here
instead of chattering with that muskrat?

77
00:06:44.143 --> 00:06:45.258
Muskrat!

78
00:06:45.383 --> 00:06:49.820
When I change back to my former self.
I will crush this army...

79
00:06:49.943 --> 00:06:53.219
and take Elora Danan
to Tir Asleen...

80
00:06:53.343 --> 00:06:55.777
where she will be safe.

81
00:06:56.583 --> 00:07:00.019
Ow! What'd you bite me for?

82
00:07:00.143 --> 00:07:03.260
You need three drops of your blood
to put in the potion.

83
00:07:03.383 --> 00:07:05.021
You could've warned me.

84
00:07:06.623 --> 00:07:08.898
For beginners.
there's some pain...

85
00:07:09.023 --> 00:07:13.858
but don't let anything
break your concentration.

86
00:07:18.823 --> 00:07:21.542
Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.

87
00:07:21.663 --> 00:07:25.178
- Hello. everybody! We have arrived!
- You are saved.

88
00:07:26.183 --> 00:07:27.980
Don't interrupt.

89
00:07:29.423 --> 00:07:32.415
Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.

90
00:07:33.223 --> 00:07:35.214
What will you look like
if this works?

91
00:07:35.343 --> 00:07:37.698
- Don't interrupt.
- Sorry.

92
00:07:37.823 --> 00:07:39.620
Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.

93
00:07:39.743 --> 00:07:42.860
I am a young. beautiful woman.

94
00:07:42.983 --> 00:07:44.655
Concentrate. Willow.

95
00:07:44.783 --> 00:07:46.819
Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.

96
00:07:49.303 --> 00:07:51.294
You're losing me!

97
00:07:52.423 --> 00:07:54.653
Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.

98
00:08:00.063 --> 00:08:02.179
You all right?
Nice try. Willow.

99
00:08:10.103 --> 00:08:13.812
Farmers!
Cherlindrea sends me farmers!

100
00:08:14.943 --> 00:08:17.252
The Nelwyn
really butchered that one.

101
00:08:17.383 --> 00:08:19.135
I'm sorry. Raziel.

102
00:08:19.343 --> 00:08:20.742
You want out?

103
00:08:20.863 --> 00:08:23.331
Easy. We can pick a lock.
Come on.

104
00:08:23.463 --> 00:08:25.101
No. No. no.
Like this!

105
00:08:25.223 --> 00:08:27.179
I know what I'm doing.
It's my spear. Leave it alone.

106
00:08:27.303 --> 00:08:29.533
Let me do it.

107
00:08:29.663 --> 00:08:31.460
Out of the way. rodents.

108
00:08:32.703 --> 00:08:33.772
Take your hand off that.

109
00:08:33.903 --> 00:08:38.101
You leave that alone.
you stupid. fat Daikini!

110
00:08:40.703 --> 00:08:42.933
Dust of broken hearts.

111
00:08:53.823 --> 00:08:55.495
You are free!

112
00:08:55.623 --> 00:08:56.692
Come on. Madmartigan.

113
00:08:56.823 --> 00:08:59.018
Let's get Elora Danan
out of here.

114
00:08:59.143 --> 00:09:00.895
Yeah.

115
00:09:01.023 --> 00:09:03.059
- It'll be fun.
- Come on.

116
00:09:14.903 --> 00:09:16.780
- Are you all right?
- Yeah.

117
00:09:18.263 --> 00:09:20.254
I feel good.

118
00:09:20.383 --> 00:09:22.294
The dust of broken hearts.

119
00:09:23.863 --> 00:09:25.216
Come on!

120
00:09:31.543 --> 00:09:34.455
- Let me see!
- Let me see. You always see.

121
00:09:34.583 --> 00:09:36.892
There's Elora. right there.
on those furs.

122
00:09:39.263 --> 00:09:42.619
Hey. wait! Leave this to us.
It's too dangerous for you.

123
00:09:42.743 --> 00:09:46.736
Only one of us should go in there.
I know what I'm doing.

124
00:10:16.463 --> 00:10:18.977
Wait. No. no!

125
00:10:29.703 --> 00:10:32.376
- I love you.
- Madmartigan!

126
00:10:32.503 --> 00:10:35.301
What are you doing?
Get the baby!

127
00:10:35.423 --> 00:10:36.697
Come on!

128
00:10:51.583 --> 00:10:53.539
Wake from this hateful sleep.

129
00:10:53.663 --> 00:10:55.893
It deprives me of your beauty.

130
00:10:57.263 --> 00:11:00.539
- The beauty of your eyes...
- One move. jackass...

131
00:11:00.663 --> 00:11:03.382
and you really will be a woman.

132
00:11:03.503 --> 00:11:09.021
You are my sun! My moon!
My starlit sky.

133
00:11:09.143 --> 00:11:12.658
Without you. I dwell in darkness.
I love you.

134
00:11:14.143 --> 00:11:15.576
What are you doing here?

135
00:11:15.703 --> 00:11:18.854
Your power has enchanted me.
I stand helpless against it.

136
00:11:18.983 --> 00:11:20.780
Come to me now.

137
00:11:20.903 --> 00:11:23.212
Tonight. let me worship you
in my arms.

138
00:11:23.343 --> 00:11:25.903
- Get away from me!
- I love you!

139
00:11:26.023 --> 00:11:28.332
Stop saying that!

140
00:11:28.463 --> 00:11:32.502
How can I stop the beating of my heart?
It pounds like never before.

141
00:11:32.623 --> 00:11:35.057
- Out of fear.
- Out of love!

142
00:11:35.183 --> 00:11:37.538
I can stop it.
I'll kill you.

143
00:11:37.663 --> 00:11:39.619
Death. next to love.
is a trivial thing.

144
00:11:43.143 --> 00:11:45.498
Your touch is worth 100.000 deaths.

145
00:11:50.223 --> 00:11:51.702
What goes on here?

146
00:11:56.623 --> 00:11:58.500
Deceiver!

147
00:12:00.063 --> 00:12:01.781
Stop him!

148
00:12:10.423 --> 00:12:12.891
Get me out!

149
00:12:22.943 --> 00:12:24.899
You are great!

150
00:12:27.903 --> 00:12:29.495
Get on that shield!

151
00:12:46.143 --> 00:12:48.020
After them!

152
00:13:00.903 --> 00:13:02.222
They're getting away!

153
00:13:11.143 --> 00:13:13.213
- Follow me. Rool.
- Where are you?

154
00:13:13.343 --> 00:13:14.981
I don't know.

155
00:13:16.063 --> 00:13:17.940
Oh. no!
Where did everybody go?

156
00:13:18.063 --> 00:13:19.940
Maybe it was something we said.

157
00:14:55.623 --> 00:14:57.500
What the hell happened up there?

158
00:14:57.623 --> 00:14:59.579
You started spouting poetry.

159
00:14:59.703 --> 00:15:02.137
- Poetry?
- Yeah.

160
00:15:02.263 --> 00:15:05.221
"I love you. Sorsha.
I worship you. Sorsha."

161
00:15:05.343 --> 00:15:07.254
You almost got us killed!

162
00:15:07.383 --> 00:15:09.135
"I love you. Sorsha"?

163
00:15:09.263 --> 00:15:11.538
I don't love her.
She kicked me in the face.

164
00:15:11.663 --> 00:15:14.097
I hate her! Don't I?

165
00:15:17.063 --> 00:15:19.338
Kael! Kael!

166
00:15:19.463 --> 00:15:21.021
Nockmaar soldiers!

167
00:15:23.943 --> 00:15:25.979
Hide! Get the children!
Come on!

168
00:15:28.903 --> 00:15:31.133
- Hide! Get the children!
- They're after us!

169
00:15:31.263 --> 00:15:34.733
- We need a place to hide.
- Come on. Follow me. Quick!

170
00:15:50.623 --> 00:15:53.262
I knew you'd get out
of that rattrap.

171
00:15:55.663 --> 00:15:57.540
You left me to die. Airk.

172
00:15:57.663 --> 00:16:00.735
I probably saved your life.
We were slaughtered. and I lost a lot...

173
00:16:00.863 --> 00:16:01.739
Quiet!

174
00:16:04.223 --> 00:16:06.020
Tear this village apart!

175
00:16:06.743 --> 00:16:09.018
Look everywhere!

176
00:16:09.143 --> 00:16:10.292
Find the child!

177
00:16:44.703 --> 00:16:47.536
Tell Sorsha
I search the north bank!

178
00:16:47.663 --> 00:16:48.812
Yes. General.

179
00:17:02.103 --> 00:17:04.014
Quiet!

180
00:17:22.663 --> 00:17:25.496
- Sorsha!
- Back.

181
00:17:26.103 --> 00:17:27.172
Back!

182
00:17:33.663 --> 00:17:34.891
Back.

183
00:17:36.623 --> 00:17:39.501
- Keep the baby quiet.
- She needs to be changed.

184
00:17:40.303 --> 00:17:42.055
- Nockmaar scum!
- You'll never defeat us.

185
00:17:42.183 --> 00:17:43.775
- Give up the baby!
- Shut up!

186
00:17:45.783 --> 00:17:49.093
- Why does Bavmorda want this baby?
- She's a princess.

187
00:17:49.223 --> 00:17:51.783
- We're taking her to Tir Asleen.
- Tir Asleen?

188
00:17:51.903 --> 00:17:53.780
Even if you could find it. peck...

189
00:17:53.903 --> 00:17:56.133
she's right... you'd never
get past the Nockmaar army.

190
00:17:56.263 --> 00:17:59.938
There's an even bigger army
at Tir Asleen. if we can get there.

191
00:18:04.383 --> 00:18:06.977
I've lost more than half my men
fighting Bavmorda.

192
00:18:07.103 --> 00:18:08.980
Now you and this peck
are gonna take her on?

193
00:18:10.103 --> 00:18:12.697
You always told me you served
no one. Madmartigan.

194
00:18:12.823 --> 00:18:14.700
Since when are you a crusader?

195
00:18:16.903 --> 00:18:18.859
He's not gonna help you. peck.

196
00:18:20.103 --> 00:18:22.253
He's a worthless thief.

197
00:18:23.343 --> 00:18:25.652
I'm not a thief. Airk.

198
00:18:25.783 --> 00:18:27.296
He's not a thief.

199
00:18:29.783 --> 00:18:30.772
Are you?

200
00:18:44.783 --> 00:18:47.058
I serve the Nelwyn. Airk.

201
00:18:52.943 --> 00:18:55.411
- Want to come with us?
- You'll never make it.

202
00:18:57.343 --> 00:18:59.573
Then once again
we say goodbye.

203
00:19:12.423 --> 00:19:15.654
- Over here!
- Sorsha!

204
00:19:15.783 --> 00:19:17.933
Weapons down or she's dead!

205
00:19:31.943 --> 00:19:33.820
Get to your horses!
After them!

206
00:20:18.143 --> 00:20:20.498
This way!
This way!

207
00:20:20.623 --> 00:20:23.183
As the crow flies. you fools!

208
00:20:29.823 --> 00:20:32.496
- You're holding me too tight!
- I don't want you to get away.

209
00:20:32.623 --> 00:20:36.502
Why? Because I'm your sun.
your moon. your starlit sky?

210
00:20:38.783 --> 00:20:40.739
Get your hair out of my face
or I'll chop it off.

211
00:20:44.623 --> 00:20:46.261
Did I really...

212
00:20:46.383 --> 00:20:48.339
Did I really say
those things last night?

213
00:20:48.463 --> 00:20:51.421
- In your tent?
- You said you loved me.

214
00:20:51.543 --> 00:20:53.898
- I don't remember that.
- You lied to me!

215
00:20:54.023 --> 00:20:55.138
No. I...

216
00:20:56.383 --> 00:20:58.658
I just wasn't myself last night.

217
00:20:58.783 --> 00:21:02.253
I suppose my power enchanted you
and you were helpless against it.

218
00:21:03.543 --> 00:21:05.613
- Sort of.
- Then what?

219
00:21:06.743 --> 00:21:09.894
- It went away.
- Went away?

220
00:21:10.023 --> 00:21:12.821
"I dwell in darkness without you."
and it went away?

221
00:21:12.943 --> 00:21:14.581
Yeah.

222
00:21:35.303 --> 00:21:37.055
Hurry! Kael's coming!

223
00:21:41.463 --> 00:21:43.613
Madmartigan. come on! Now!

224
00:21:51.343 --> 00:21:53.061
Madmartigan. come on!

225
00:21:54.863 --> 00:21:57.502
They're coming! Away!

226
00:21:57.623 --> 00:21:58.738
Go on!

227
00:22:16.143 --> 00:22:17.622
Whoa! Whoa!

228
00:22:19.183 --> 00:22:20.616
This way!

229
00:22:26.543 --> 00:22:30.172
Tir Asleen!
At last. Tir Asleen!

230
00:22:40.663 --> 00:22:41.937
Hello?

231
00:22:43.823 --> 00:22:45.302
Hello?

232
00:22:49.303 --> 00:22:50.622
Hello?

233
00:22:52.463 --> 00:22:54.977
Why did I listen to you. peck?

234
00:22:55.103 --> 00:22:58.413
"Everything will be all right
once we get to Tir Asleen."

235
00:22:59.303 --> 00:23:02.022
The only army around is the one that's
about to ride across this valley...

236
00:23:02.143 --> 00:23:03.895
and wipe us out!

237
00:23:04.023 --> 00:23:06.901
But Cherlindrea said
we'd be safe here.

238
00:23:07.663 --> 00:23:10.575
Safe? Look at these people.

239
00:23:10.703 --> 00:23:14.412
This place is cursed. peck.
It's falling apart. Open your eyes!

240
00:23:14.543 --> 00:23:15.817
And it...

241
00:23:18.103 --> 00:23:20.014
Trolls.

242
00:23:22.943 --> 00:23:24.899
I hate trolls.

243
00:23:25.663 --> 00:23:27.938
This is the work of Bavmorda.

244
00:23:36.783 --> 00:23:39.217
Willow? The wand.

245
00:23:39.343 --> 00:23:42.540
- Turn me back into my human form.
- Are you sure?

246
00:24:00.063 --> 00:24:01.132
Good.

247
00:24:08.423 --> 00:24:10.379
Hurry. Willow.
Transform me.

248
00:24:10.503 --> 00:24:13.301
I can't do it.
I'm just not a sorcerer.

249
00:24:13.423 --> 00:24:19.020
But you can be.
Speak and be one with the words.

250
00:24:19.143 --> 00:24:22.135
Avalorium greenan...

251
00:24:22.663 --> 00:24:25.416
